The first time I met DC, he told me we’d be friends one day. 

Some 12 years later, I’m proud to call him one of my very best friends.

What an honor & joy it has been to do this show with him over the past year+. 

Thanks to all who watched and supported.

node.text:
Oh my word.

A.J. McKee has submitted Patricio Pitbull in the first. Standing guillotine. No tap. Out cold.

The fight and moment lived up to the hype, despite being short. 

This is the moment and the fighter Bellator has been waiting on for years now.

A superstar is born. 18-0. New 145 champ. 

(🎥 @bellatormma, @shosports)

node.text:
Amanda Nunes x Julianna Peña on Aug. 7 is off, per sources. Nunes forced to withdraw due to COVID. They are hoping to reschedule the bantamweight title bout later this year.

UFC 265 now moves forward with one title fight: Derrick Lewis x Ciryl Gane for the interim heavyweight title.
